{"tid":1244358,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我知好囉嗦 但請大家真係要再確認多次選民資格","createTime":"2019-06-20T00:59:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T01:31:48.000Z","uid":262458,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4215f66c7cdde125daccb999f5a3944c230d93a7","tid":1244358,"uid":262458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T00:59:35.000Z","msg":"第一次開post,打得怪的話請見諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢幾日係咁網傳原來<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">選民資格</span></span>都會被<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">DQ</span></span><br />\n半信半疑之下，自己及身邊好多人都開始上網查多次以確保自己依然持有效選民資格<br />\n結果多於一人喺查詢結果下發現<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以下紅字</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uo3rnt6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fuo3rnt6.png&h=8b569da3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0pEewnx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0pEewnx.png&h=4fc3309e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我唔知係限期前唔覆係咪就等於無左個選民資料，係的話真係好大鑊<br />\n如遇以上情況 我建議：<br />\n1. <span style=\"font-size: large;\">即刻打電話</span>上去選舉事務處，叫佢地<span style=\"font-size: large;\">立刻email需要回覆嘅信件俾你</span>，唔好再用電郵同佢慢慢溝通，亦唔好再等佢郵寄俾你（但你可能要print番封信出黎覆佢），否則會過deadline<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Va7vPcW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVa7vPcW.png&h=d1b0b9fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2. 個電話可能要打多幾次先有人聽，如果個職員已經承諾會補發email俾你，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記得問佢個名，員工號碼&amp;幾時會send</span></span>，最好錄音<br />\n（對住呢個政府，被害妄想症無可能唔病發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n3. 鼓勵身邊朋友去<a href=\"https://www2.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/mob/welcome.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.voterinfo.gov.hk%2Fbd_reovi%2FOVIES%2Fjsp%2Fmob%2Fwelcome.jsp&d=ZVysXiw7s3azMdswkJgtbIXq8Qv2IeoILbHjSh09rgU%3D&h=38f0b404\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/mob/welcome.jsp</a> check多次個選民資格，最好cap screen個結果版面<br />\n4. 身邊有唔熟悉電腦或唔識處理呢d程序嘅人，做多一步，教/幫佢check埋，多佢一票好重要！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">血債票償</span>，大家真係唔好懶，做多一步！有其他建議嘅巴打絲打歡迎留言補充！<br />\n香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df7570fb00ed0a874084d6d7483330826c6db8e7","tid":1244358,"uid":155107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T01:00:19.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"e2cc38cefe15bbbe9e0e784010f73cbe0f86d08a","tid":1244358,"uid":808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T01:02:39.000Z","msg":"尋日交左form做選民登記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"589dd8c4f88c8ac5a15400d9a3d1e7489041887f","tid":1244358,"uid":22318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T01:03:23.000Z","msg":"我比人dq左係咪正路再登記多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b684cb5d317c67f816f486f9fbb4c93c2a9802ee","tid":1244358,"uid":126541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T01:30:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sCzx2Mq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsCzx2Mq.png&h=17d72a45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家改唔切地址 可以去舊地址投票呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1aebc2172fbd94a336eede307659ac29f2d29ba","tid":1244358,"uid":223609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T01:31:48.000Z","msg":"PUSH!"}]}